including Pounds 2.66m from acquisitions. The figures included almost a full
contribution from Accountancy Tutors, acquired in January.
Pre-tax profits doubled to Pounds 1.21m (Pounds 602,000) but the placing and
open offer to fund the purchase left earnings per share lower at 4.37p
against 5.36p.
However, the group remains confident of prospects and the interim dividend
is raised to 1.94p (1.76p).
